reviewText: I am a big fan of non-fiction movies.  This DVD is a real bargain.  Each movie is well worth the price of these four.  Highly recommended!
very good set of movies  especially for the price
Great movies, well worth the bargain price.

I love these bundles of Lifetime movies. My wife loves watching these on the lifetime movie network. I get them for her as a small gift for her birthday, valentine's day or Christmas.

She makes me watch them with her, but that is not the fault of the movies themselves.

Can you really go wrong with Lifetime movies???
NO! And these movies are so much fun.
You will enjoy four great movies at one low price.
